To install ext3Viewer, just follow the steps:

   1) Change directory into the top of the ext3Viewer source tree

   2) If you want to install ext3Viewer in a particular place, change the
      INSTALL_DIR, BIN_DIR and MAN_DIR constants in the Makefile.
      Else it will be installed in /usr/local/share/ext3Viewer.

   3)  Compile the program

    Run `make`

   5)  Install the program

    Run `make install' as root
   
   6) You can now run `ext3Viewer` or `gext3Viewer` as a normal user. 
      For help type `man ext3Viewer` or visit our online documentation 
      at http://ext3viewer.free.fr.

